data.description:
Gorgeous, completely renovated home in renown Allen ISD! Fresh modern renovation with contemporary modern finishes, lots of natural light, and smart home features throughout. Modern mahogany front door, high vaulted ceiling in formal living room, open concept dining area with modern
chandelier, beautiful kitchen with white shake cabinets, stainless appliances with gas range and quartz
counters, spacious den with gas fireplace! All new LOW-E windows, smart electric window blinds, smart home locks and lights, recent 35 Year Roof Warranty, Foundation Lifetime Warranty, new backup home generator, recent HVAC and water heater, fresh landscaping, and new 8' Fence with Electric Gate! Overall, beautiful home in great school district in Allen!
